</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>DeviceId</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>is the unique device ID of the DisplayPort TX core instance.</para></parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
<simplesect kind="return"><para><itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>XST_SUCCESS if the DisplayPort TX&apos;s registers are at their default reset values.</para></listitem><listitem><para>XST_FAILURE if the DisplayPort TX&apos;s registers do not match their default values or no DisplayPort TX instance was found.</para></listitem></itemizedlist>
